The paper is about bug localization in software maintenance, which is a subfield of software engineering (cs.SE). The proposed method uses word embeddings, which are commonly used in information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The method also involves network regularization, which is a technique used in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Therefore, these five sub-categories are the most likely ones for this paper.
